="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Lorde-Girl-In-Red-The-National@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Lorde-Girl-In-Red-The-National@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Lorde-Girl-In-Red-The-National@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Lorde-Girl-In-Red-The-National@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Lorde-Girl-In-Red-The-National@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Lorde-Girl-In-Red-The-National@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>更多艺术家将出现在即将推出的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/talking-heads">Talking Heads</a>致敬专辑中，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lorde">Lorde</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/girl-in-red">Girl In Red</a>等。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/concert-films-taylor-swift-eras-talking-heads-beyonce-renaissance-3531888"><b>音乐会电影如何成为大生意（再次）</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>该项目于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-announce-return-with-cover-on-talking-heads-tribute-album-3568542">上个月首次宣布，当时 A24 确认专辑即将推出</a>，其中 16 位艺术家将分享他们自己翻唱的 Talking Heads 经典作品。</p><p>第一批确认参与的艺术家之一是美国流行朋克偶像<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">Paramore</a> ，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-announce-return-with-cover-on-talking-heads-tribute-album-3568542">被确认将翻唱《Burning Down The House》</a>作为原声带的一部分。</p><p>这一消息是在乐队清除所有社交媒体账户后发布的，导致了分手的谣言。他们的第一个回帖是一段视频，其中女主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hayley-williams">海莉·威廉姆斯 (Hayley Williams)</a>领取了一个送到她家的包裹。打开后，她发现了 Talking Heads 主唱大卫·伯恩<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/DAVID-BYRNE">(David Byrne</a> ) 标志性的超大西装，他在乐队的演唱会电影<em>《Stop Making Sense》</em>中就曾穿着这套西装。</p><p>然后，她从音箱顶部拉出一盘磁带，播放着“烧毁房子”。帕拉莫尔对这首歌的翻唱作为预告片中的背景音频。今天（1月31日）该曲目已完整分享，请在下面查看。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="帕拉莫尔 - 烧毁房子（官方展示台）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qrjHhIGl90I?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>除了分享新的 Paramore 封面外，A24 Music 还宣布将有更多艺术家参与合辑<em>《Everybody&#39;s Getting Involved: A Tribute to Talking Heads Stop Making Sense》。</em></p><p>其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">Miley Cyrus</a> 、Lorde、The National、Girl In Red、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blondshell">Blondshell</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/badbadnotgood">BADBADNOTGOOD 等</a>。</p><p> The Cavemen、Jean Dawson、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kevin-abstract">Kevin Abstract</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-linda-lindas">The Linda Lindas</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/teezo-touchdown">Teezo Touchdown</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/toro-y-moi">Toro y Moi</a>也出现在其中。</p><p>这张专辑是为了庆祝乔纳森·戴米 (Jonathan Demme) 的标志性同名音乐会电影最近重新发行，旨在向新一代歌迷介绍 Talking Heads 的音乐，并为他们的曲目提供新的诠释。长期粉丝。</p><p>该专辑的正式发行日期尚未公布。 </p><figure id="attachment_3579961" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3579961" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3579961" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Stop-making-sense-tribute-album-artowrk@2000x2000.jpeg" alt="“停止有意义：致敬专辑”艺术品" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Stop-making-sense-tribute-album-artowrk@2000x2000.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Stop-making-sense-tribute-album-artowrk@2000x2000-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Stop-making-sense-tribute-album-artowrk@2000x2000-400x400.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Stop-making-sense-tribute-album-artowrk@2000x2000-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Stop-making-sense-tribute-album-artowrk@2000x2000-696x696.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Stop-making-sense-tribute-album-artowrk@2000x2000-1392x1392.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Stop-making-sense-tribute-album-artowrk@2000x2000-1068x1068.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3579961" class="wp-caption-text"> “停止有意义：致敬专辑”艺术品。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>本月早些时候，经证实， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-stop-making-sense-is-returning-to-cinemas-again-3572947"><em>《Stop Making Sense</em> 》的改版将重返各地影院</a>。</p><p>周末（1 月 27 日）重返电影院，“每月驻场放映”已安排在“选定城市”，包括伦敦、纽约、洛杉矶、奥斯汀、芝加哥、旧金山和多伦多。</p><p>此外，粉丝们还可以在每次放映时购买《Stop Making Sense》的珍藏版蓝光光盘以及新的特别商品。</p><p>在最近的一次采访中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-david-byrne-says-he-felt-removed-re-watching-himself-in-stop-making-sense-3557692">大卫·伯恩表示，在《别再讲道理》中重新观看自己在银幕上的经历，让他感到“恍惚”</a> 。 “这几乎就像我在看一个角色，”他解释道。</p><p> Talking Heads 鼓手 Chris Franz <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-chris-franz-hints-at-further-potential-reunion-3507373">去年 10 月曾暗示，该乐队未来可能会进一步重聚</a>。这位音乐家上个月在 TIFF 上与他的前乐队成员一起参加了问答，这是他们 20 多年来首次一起公开露面。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/talking-heads-on-a-potential-reunion-were-just-savouring-the-moment-3502089">蒂娜·韦茅斯 (Tina Weymouth) 表示，Talking Heads 在讨论潜在的回归时“只是在享受这一刻”</a> ：“我们很高兴它产生了持续 40 年的美妙事物。我们并没有真正展望太远的未来。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lorde-the-national-girl-in-red-feature-on-stop-making-sense-tribute-album-everyones-getting-involved-3579958">众星云集的“Stop Making Sense”致敬专辑“Everyone&#39;s Getting Involved”中的 Post Lorde、The National、Girl In Red 等歌曲</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
